OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering showers will soon die out to
OL,7,Fleave some late sunny spells this
OL,8,Fevening. Remaining dry overnight with
OL,9,Flong clear spells. Winds becoming
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright start with sunny
OL,13,Fspells but cloud increasing through
OL,14,Fthe morning with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fedging east, although the eastern
OL,16,FBorders remains dry and bright until
OL,17,Flate afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
