OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,6,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,7,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,8,FSunny spells and just a few showers
OL,9,FMonday, but cloudier Tuesday with
OL,10,Foccasionally heavy rain or thundery
OL,11,Fshowers.
